<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/MorvanZhou/tutorials/blob/master/sklearnTUT/sk6_model_attribute_method.py" target="_blank">зӣёе…ід»Јз Ғ</a></li>
</ul>

<p>дёҠж¬ЎеӯҰдәҶ  <code class="highlighter-rouge">Sklearn</code> дёӯзҡ„ <code class="highlighter-rouge">data sets</code>пјҢд»ҠеӨ©жқҘзңӢ Model зҡ„еұһжҖ§е’ҢеҠҹиғҪгҖӮ</p>

<p>иҝҷйҮҢд»Ҙ <code class="highlighter-rouge">LinearRegressor</code> дёәдҫӢпјҢжүҖд»Ҙе…ҲеҜје…ҘеҢ…пјҢж•°жҚ®пјҢиҝҳжңүжЁЎеһӢгҖӮ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">datasets</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">sklearn.linear_model</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">LinearRegression</span>

<span class="n">loaded_data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">datasets</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">load_boston</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">data_X</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">loaded_data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">data</span>
<span class="n">data_y</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">loaded_data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">target</span>

<span class="n">model</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">LinearRegression</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="и®ӯз»ғе’Ңйў„жөӢ">и®ӯз»ғе’Ңйў„жөӢ
  <a href="/tutorials/machine-learning/sklearn/2-4-model-attributes/#и®ӯз»ғе’Ңйў„жөӢ" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<p>жҺҘдёӢжқҘ <code class="highlighter-rouge">model.fit</code> е’Ң <code class="highlighter-rouge">model.predict</code> е°ұеұһдәҺ Model зҡ„еҠҹиғҪпјҢз”ЁжқҘи®ӯз»ғжЁЎеһӢпјҢз”Ёи®ӯз»ғеҘҪзҡ„жЁЎеһӢйў„жөӢгҖӮ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">model</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fit</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data_X</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">data_y</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">model</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">predict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data_X</span><span class="p">[:</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">:]))</span>

<span class="s">"""
[ 30.00821269  25.0298606   30.5702317   28.60814055]
"""</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="еҸӮж•°е’ҢеҲҶж•°">еҸӮж•°е’ҢеҲҶж•°
  <a href="/tutorials/machine-learning/sklearn/2-4-model-attributes/#еҸӮж•°е’ҢеҲҶж•°" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<p>з„¶еҗҺпјҢ<code class="highlighter-rouge">model.coef_</code> е’Ң <code class="highlighter-rouge">model.intercept_ </code> еұһдәҺ Model зҡ„еұһжҖ§пјҢ
дҫӢеҰӮеҜ№дәҺ <code class="highlighter-rouge">LinearRegressor</code> иҝҷдёӘжЁЎеһӢпјҢиҝҷдёӨдёӘеұһжҖ§еҲҶеҲ«иҫ“еҮәжЁЎеһӢзҡ„ж–ңзҺҮе’ҢжҲӘи·қпјҲдёҺyиҪҙзҡ„дәӨзӮ№пјүгҖӮ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">model</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">coef_</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">model</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">intercept_</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="s">"""
