<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">model.get_params()</code> д№ҹжҳҜеҠҹиғҪпјҢе®ғеҸҜд»ҘеҸ–еҮәд№ӢеүҚе®ҡд№үзҡ„еҸӮж•°гҖӮ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">model</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">get_params</span><span class="p">())</span>


<span class="s">"""
{'copy_X': True, 'normalize': False, 'n_jobs': 1, 'fit_intercept': True}
"""</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">model.score(data_X, data_y)</code> е®ғеҸҜд»ҘеҜ№ Model з”Ё <code class="highlighter-rouge">R^2</code> зҡ„ж–№ејҸиҝӣиЎҢжү“еҲҶпјҢиҫ“еҮәзІҫзЎ®еәҰгҖӮе…ідәҺ <code class="highlighter-rouge">R^2 coefficient of determination</code> еҸҜд»ҘжҹҘзңӢ <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_determination" target="_blank">wiki</a></p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">model</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">score</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data_X</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">data_y</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="c1"># R^2 coefficient of determination
</span>
<span class="s">"""
0.740607742865
"""</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

